features: 👍2 Detachable & Dimmable Fill Lights: 3 different color modes available: warm light, natural light, and white light. Each mode has 2 brightness levels, offering a total of 6 options to meet your needs in various situations. The 2 lights provide a wider range of illumination and are suitable for different levels of darkness.

👍2023 Upgraded Stable Tripod: With its built-in umbrella-shaped tripod structure and longer tripod counterweight base, it offers greater stability compared to other traditional selfie sticks. It can be transformed into a desktop tripod in just 1 second, and it can also be extended to stand on the ground, allowing you to capture full-body shots or group photos without holding the stick.

👍More Possibilities with Exceptionally Versatile and Long: The 7-section telescopic pole can be adjusted to a maximum length of 44.9 inches, surpassing most others on the market, granting you an expansive field of view. With the combination of 180°adjustment and 360° rotation, you can effortlessly find your optimal angle, capturing vast landscapes or capturing cherished moments with your loved ones.

💕Capturing the Beauty of Moment with Ease: Featuring an embedded anti-loss remote design, this selfie stick can be effortlessly changed, whether held in hand or used for remote photography. It offers a remarkable Bluetooth range of up to 10 meters, allowing you to take photos from a distance. When a remote controller is not required, simply toggle the switch to conserve energy effectively, extending the battery life (an additional replaceable lithium battery is included).

🎁Compact & Lightweight Design for Portability: With a small size of 8.3 inches and lightweight of 0.47 lb, this selfie stick can easily fit into any handbag or backpack, making it a perfect companion for travel, daily life, and outdoor activities. It's an ideal gift choice for your loved ones, Leave precious memories.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very handy for taking photos and videos with family and friends!
reviews.reviewText: Very easy to set up and use with the lights and bluetooth. The different light settings are nice. I like the multipurpose use (selfie stick/tripod). Design is such that the product can be easily stored as it compacts nicely. Only concern is how easy it is to get your skin caught when closing the tripod legs, although I believe there was a warning about that in the instruction manual.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I LOVE this tripod, but have no clue how to use the light
reviews.reviewText: The tripod is amazing!! It fits super small and fit into my purses and small backpacks, it's lightweight and the selfie clicker worked just fine for me. The only thing I couldn't figure out for the life of me was how to work the selfie lights, so I gave up on them and didn't even wind up bringing them along on my adventures.It's sturdy enough, I definitely had it fall over on me once or twice in some windy and unstable place, and after it fell one time, the phone holder part is ever so slightly off-level. However, this is honestly the best travel tripod/selfie stick i've had because of it's size and portability. It doesn't get SUPER tall but I really loved it anyway. Great for solo travelers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I wanted Great Selfie Stick

Bewertung: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ (5/5 Sterne)Ich habe vor kurzem den Selfie Stick Stativ mit 2 Fülllicht erworben und bin absolut begeistert von diesem Produkt. Hier sind einige Gründe, warum ich es uneingeschränkt empfehlen kann:Vielseitige Verwendung: Die Kombination aus Selfie Stick und Stativ bietet eine beeindruckende Vielseitigkeit. Ob für Selfies, Gruppenfotos oder Videoaufnahmen - dieses Produkt erfüllt alle Bedürfnisse.Fülllicht für perfekte Ausleuchtung: Die zwei Fülllichter sind ein echtes Highlight. Sie sorgen für eine hervorragende Ausleuchtung in jeder Situation, sei es bei schlechten Lichtverhältnissen oder für professionell aussehende Aufnahmen.Robust und Stabil: Die Verarbeitungsqualität des Sticks und des Stativs ist ausgezeichnet. Das Material ist robust, und die Beine des Stativs bieten eine stabile Basis für alle Arten von Aufnahmen.Einfache Bedienung: Die Bedienung des Selfie Sticks ist intuitiv. Die Bluetooth-Verbindung funktioniert einwandfrei, und die Tasten sind gut platziert. Kein kompliziertes Setup, einfach einschalten und loslegen.Kompakt und leicht: Das Design ist nicht nur funktional, sondern auch äußerst kompakt. Der Selfie Stick lässt sich problemlos zusammenklappen und in der Tasche verstauen, was ihn ideal für unterwegs macht.Insgesamt bin ich äußerst zufrieden mit dem Selfie Stick Stativ mit 2 Fülllicht. Es ist nicht nur ein praktisches Werkzeug für tolle Fotos und Videos, sondern auch ein erschwingliches und hochwertiges Gadget. Klare Kaufempfehlung!
